[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":542},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fother\u002F20250605\u002F2959757908\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fother\u002F20250605\u002F2959757908\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fother\u002F20250605\u002F2959757908\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fother\u002F20250605\u002F2959757908\u002F":517,"related:\u002Fother\u002F20250605\u002F2959757908\u002F":526},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2025\u002F06\u002F05\u002Fwhy-port-3000-explained\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":500,"date":501,"description":502,"extension":503,"lang":504,"meta":505,"navigation":79,"path":506,"readingMinutes":507,"seo":508,"standalone":509,"stem":510,"tags":511,"tldr":513,"updated":514,"url":515,"__hash__":516},"content\u002F雜談\u002F為什麼大家都用 3000？一文搞懂 Port 的用途與選擇.md","Port 是什麼？為什麼大家都用 3000？一文搞懂用途與選擇","2959757908",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":494},"minimark",[11,18,28,32,35,39,42,133,150,153,169,172,175,207,214,244,247,251,254,257,260,316,319,330,340,346,352,357,369,372,376,379,398,401,404,410,433,436,463,466,487,490],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":6,"src":17},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fport\u002FChatGPT%20Image%202025%E5%B9%B46%E6%9C%885%E6%97%A5%20%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%8810_55_32.png",[19,20,21],"blockquote",{},[12,22,23,27],{},[24,25,26],"strong",{},"Note","\nPort（通訊埠）是用來區分電腦上不同服務的編號。一台電腦只有一組 IP 但同時跑多個服務（Web、Database、FTP 等），靠 Port 區分要連到哪個服務。3000 沒有特殊規範，純粹是 Node.js 框架社群的慣例。",[29,30,31],"h2",{"id":31},"前言",[12,33,34],{},"最近有不少學生問我：「Port 是什麼？為什麼大家都用 3000？」與其一個個解釋，不如一次寫清楚：什麼是 Port、怎麼選、怎麼查，用對了不再踩雷。",[29,36,38],{"id":37},"port-是什麼","Port 是什麼？",[12,40,41],{},"Port 中文是通訊埠，如果你是一名開發者，應該會很常看到以下的訊息",[43,44,49],"pre",{"className":45,"code":46,"language":47,"meta":48,"style":48},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","Server is running at http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:3000\n\nServer is running at http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:8000\n\nServer is running at http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:8080\n\nServer is running at http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:5000\n","bash","",[50,51,52,74,81,95,100,114,119],"code",{"__ignoreMap":48},[53,54,57,61,65,68,71],"span",{"class":55,"line":56},"line",1,[53,58,60],{"class":59},"s_sBn","Server",[53,62,64],{"class":63},"sTRMh"," is",[53,66,67],{"class":63}," running",[53,69,70],{"class":63}," at",[53,72,73],{"class":63}," http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:3000\n",[53,75,77],{"class":55,"line":76},2,[53,78,80],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":79},true,"\n",[53,82,84,86,88,90,92],{"class":55,"line":83},3,[53,85,60],{"class":59},[53,87,64],{"class":63},[53,89,67],{"class":63},[53,91,70],{"class":63},[53,93,94],{"class":63}," http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:8000\n",[53,96,98],{"class":55,"line":97},4,[53,99,80],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":79},[53,101,103,105,107,109,111],{"class":55,"line":102},5,[53,104,60],{"class":59},[53,106,64],{"class":63},[53,108,67],{"class":63},[53,110,70],{"class":63},[53,112,113],{"class":63}," http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:8080\n",[53,115,117],{"class":55,"line":116},6,[53,118,80],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":79},[53,120,122,124,126,128,130],{"class":55,"line":121},7,[53,123,60],{"class":59},[53,125,64],{"class":63},[53,127,67],{"class":63},[53,129,70],{"class":63},[53,131,132],{"class":63}," http:\u002F\u002Flocalhost:5000\n",[12,134,135,136,139,140,139,143,139,146,149],{},"在這邊我們所指的 Port 就是 ",[50,137,138],{},"3000","、",[50,141,142],{},"8000",[50,144,145],{},"8080",[50,147,148],{},"5000"," 這些數字。",[12,151,152],{},"那麼為什麼要有這些 Port 呢？我們都知道一台電腦對外提供服務時，都會有一組 IP 位址，但是單純持有這個 IP 位址就可以知道這個電腦提供了哪些服務嗎？答案是不能的，畢竟一台電腦上你可能有多個服務在運行，例如：",[154,155,156,160,163,166],"ul",{},[157,158,159],"li",{},"Web Server",[157,161,162],{},"Database Server",[157,164,165],{},"Game Server",[157,167,168],{},"FTP Server",[12,170,171],{},"這些服務如果都透過同一個 IP 位址來提供服務的話，使用者就無法知道要連接到哪個服務，所以就需要 Port 來區分這些服務，也因此衍生出「Port」這個概念。",[12,173,174],{},"舉例來講：",[154,176,177,188,195,201],{},[157,178,179,180,183,184,187],{},"Web Server 通常會使用 ",[50,181,182],{},"80"," Port（HTTP）或 ",[50,185,186],{},"443"," Port（HTTPS）",[157,189,190,191,194],{},"Database Server 通常會使用 ",[50,192,193],{},"3306"," Port",[157,196,197,198,194],{},"Game Server 通常會使用 ",[50,199,200],{},"25565",[157,202,203,204,194],{},"FTP Server 通常會使用 ",[50,205,206],{},"21",[12,208,209,210,213],{},"當你的 IP 位址假設是 ",[50,211,212],{},"192.168.1.1","，那麼這些服務的完整連接方式就會是：",[154,215,216,226,232,238],{},[157,217,218,219,222,223],{},"Web Server: ",[50,220,221],{},"http:\u002F\u002F192.168.1.1:80"," 或 ",[50,224,225],{},"https:\u002F\u002F192.168.1.1:443",[157,227,228,229],{},"Database Server: ",[50,230,231],{},"mysql:\u002F\u002F192.168.1.1:3306",[157,233,234,235],{},"Game Server: ",[50,236,237],{},"tcp:\u002F\u002F192.168.1.1:25565",[157,239,240,241],{},"FTP Server: ",[50,242,243],{},"ftp:\u002F\u002F192.168.1.1:21",[12,245,246],{},"所以我們的 Port 就是用來區分這些服務的。",[29,248,250],{"id":249},"port-的選擇","Port 的選擇",[12,252,253],{},"那麼接下來另一個問題是...",[12,255,256],{},"「我怎麼知道我該選擇哪個 Port？」",[12,258,259],{},"首先我們要先了解，Port 的範圍是從 0 到 65535，而這些 Port 實際上依用途可以分成以下三類：",[261,262,263,279],"table",{},[264,265,266],"thead",{},[267,268,269,273,276],"tr",{},[270,271,272],"th",{},"Port 範圍",[270,274,275],{},"類型",[270,277,278],{},"建議用途",[280,281,282,294,305],"tbody",{},[267,283,284,288,291],{},[285,286,287],"td",{},"0–1023",[285,289,290],{},"公認埠口",[285,292,293],{},"系統或標準協定（避免使用）",[267,295,296,299,302],{},[285,297,298],{},"1024–49151",[285,300,301],{},"註冊埠口",[285,303,304],{},"常見服務，如 MySQL、Redis",[267,306,307,310,313],{},[285,308,309],{},"49152–65535",[285,311,312],{},"動態\u002F私有埠",[285,314,315],{},"本地測試、臨時用途",[12,317,318],{},"這些 Port 是隨便定義的嗎？",[12,320,321,322,329],{},"當然不是，這些 Port 都是 Internet Assigned Numbers Authority（IANA）所定義的，這些 Port 都有其特定的用途，當你不確定時，你可以到 ",[323,324,328],"a",{"href":325,"rel":326},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.iana.org\u002Fassignments\u002Fservice-names-port-numbers\u002Fservice-names-port-numbers.xhtml",[327],"nofollow","IANA 的官方網站"," 查看這些你要使用的 Port 是否已經被使用。",[12,331,332,333,336,337,194],{},"例如...你可以查詢一下 ",[50,334,335],{},"Vite"," 的 Port，Vite 預設使用 ",[50,338,339],{},"5173",[12,341,342],{},[15,343],{"alt":344,"src":345},"port","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fport\u002F20250605223921.png",[12,347,348,349,351],{},"又或者你可以試著查詢 ",[50,350,138],{}," Port，這是一個許多 Web Server 預設使用的 Port",[12,353,354],{},[15,355],{"alt":344,"src":356},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fother\u002Fport\u002F20250605224119.png",[12,358,359,360,362,363,365,366,368],{},"我們可以看到 ",[50,361,138],{}," Port 是有被登記一套軟體叫做「RemoteWare Client RemoteWare」使用的，但是後面我們還可以看到一句話「This entry records an unassigned but widespread use」，這就代表著雖然 ",[50,364,138],{}," Port 是被登記了，但是並沒有被廣泛的使用，所以我們還是可以使用 ",[50,367,138],{}," Port。",[12,370,371],{},"所以當你不確定你的 Port 該設置為多少時，你可以先查詢一下 IANA 的官方網站，看看你要使用的 Port 是否已經被使用，若查詢後這個 Port 並沒有被廣泛使用，那麼你就可以安心使用它，不用擔心踩到標準服務的地雷。",[29,373,375],{"id":374},"如何檢查-port-是否被佔用","如何檢查 Port 是否被佔用？",[12,377,378],{},"最後也分享一下我們開發上常常遇到的一個雷點",[43,380,382],{"className":45,"code":381,"language":47,"meta":48,"style":48},"Port already in use\n",[50,383,384],{"__ignoreMap":48},[53,385,386,389,392,395],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,387,388],{"class":59},"Port",[53,390,391],{"class":63}," already",[53,393,394],{"class":63}," in",[53,396,397],{"class":63}," use\n",[12,399,400],{},"這個錯誤通常代表你的 Port 已經被其他程式佔用了。",[12,402,403],{},"那麼我們該如何檢查這個 Port 是否被佔用呢？",[12,405,406,407,409],{},"假設你目前要使用的 Port 是 ",[50,408,138],{},"，那麼你可以使用以下指令來檢查：",[43,411,413],{"className":45,"code":412,"language":47,"meta":48,"style":48},"# MacOS \u002F Linux\nlsof -i :3000\n",[50,414,415,421],{"__ignoreMap":48},[53,416,417],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,418,420],{"class":419},"sQrFR","# MacOS \u002F Linux\n",[53,422,423,426,430],{"class":55,"line":76},[53,424,425],{"class":59},"lsof",[53,427,429],{"class":428},"sCcAr"," -i",[53,431,432],{"class":63}," :3000\n",[12,434,435],{},"如果是 Windows 的話，你可以使用以下指令：",[43,437,439],{"className":45,"code":438,"language":47,"meta":48,"style":48},"# Windows\nnetstat -aon | findstr :3000\n",[50,440,441,446],{"__ignoreMap":48},[53,442,443],{"class":55,"line":56},[53,444,445],{"class":419},"# Windows\n",[53,447,448,451,454,458,461],{"class":55,"line":76},[53,449,450],{"class":59},"netstat",[53,452,453],{"class":428}," -aon",[53,455,457],{"class":456},"sWyjQ"," |",[53,459,460],{"class":59}," findstr",[53,462,432],{"class":63},[12,464,465],{},"如果你發現被佔用了，你可以考慮兩種方式：",[154,467,468,478],{},[157,469,470,471,222,474,477],{},"直接改變你的 Port，例如改成 ",[50,472,473],{},"3001",[50,475,476],{},"3002"," 等等。",[157,479,480,481,486],{},"參考「",[323,482,485],{"href":483,"rel":484},"https:\u002F\u002Fisraynotarray.com\u002Fother\u002F20220117\u002F241830554\u002F",[327],"Mac 系統 Port 號被佔用的解決方式(Mac Port xxx is already in use)","」這篇文章，來釋放被佔用的 Port。",[12,488,489],{},"那麼以上就是關於 Port 的基本知識與使用方式，希望對你有所幫助哩～",[491,492,493],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}",{"title":48,"searchDepth":76,"depth":76,"links":495},[496,497,498,499],{"id":31,"depth":76,"text":31},{"id":37,"depth":76,"text":38},{"id":249,"depth":76,"text":250},{"id":374,"depth":76,"text":375},"雜談","2025-06-05 21:48:10","不少學生問我「Port 是什麼？為什麼大家都用 3000？」這一篇講清楚：Port 是什麼、保留範圍怎麼劃分、開發專案該選哪個、怎麼查被誰佔用， 看完不再踩「Port already in use」這個雷。","md","zh-Hant",{},"\u002F3000-port","3",{"title":6,"description":502},false,"雜談\u002F為什麼大家都用 3000？一文搞懂 Port 的用途與選擇",[388,512],"網路基礎",null,"2026-06-11 09:00:00","\u002Fother\u002F20250605\u002F2959757908\u002F","7uLIwmNPzVyYOw5dFsk80YN_Oj2Ot3Ix1J9PcG4monI",{"newer":518,"older":522},{"url":519,"title":520,"date":521},"\u002Flearnexp\u002F20250901\u002F2579876145\u002F","【Day 1】第一次聽見『嗶』，我的電腦世界就此展開","2025-09-01 00:00:01",{"url":523,"title":524,"date":525},"\u002Fai\u002F20250523\u002F980109919\u002F","打造 AI Agent 專屬 MCP Server：整合 GitHub Copilot Chat 的完整實作教學","2025-05-23 15:02:03",[527,532,537],{"url":528,"title":529,"date":530,"readingMinutes":531},"\u002Fother\u002F20260710\u002F2193411838\u002F","關於我做了百日挑戰「增肌減脂」這個有趣的實驗","2026-07-10 09:53:56","16",{"url":533,"title":534,"date":535,"readingMinutes":536},"\u002Fother\u002F20260623\u002F2826413095\u002F","Mac 系統監控工具就推薦用 Stats！一款免費又開源，還能看 CPU、GPU、溫度、網速的軟體","2026-06-23 10:00:00","4",{"url":538,"title":539,"date":540,"readingMinutes":541},"\u002Fother\u002F20260526\u002F2846301957\u002F","寫部落格能月入幾萬美金嗎？聊聊 Google AdSense 真實收益與計算方式","2026-05-26 21:00:00","5",1784020396745]